videos.description: Syracuse's Kiara Lewis drives to the basket and sinks the floater as the first half comes to a close against Louisville.

videos.description: Jazmine Jones has a chance for a 3-point play after she sinks the teardrop floater against Syracuse.

videos.description: Kiara Lewis is finding her groove after she splashes the clutch fadeaway triple.

videos.description: Syracuse controls the pace and upsets Louisville 59-51, earning its first win at the dome against a top-5 team since 1996.
videos.headline: Syracuse upsets No. 5 Louisville
